text: The Nocatee Parkway is a highway in Jacksonville, Florida, in the community of Nocatee, and in the counties of Duval and St. Johns. The road provides easy access to Jacksonville, Interstate 95 (I-95) and State Route 9B (Future I-795) for the people in Nocatee and elsewhere. The parkway is also a hurricane evacuation route. ==References== Category:Jacksonville, Florida
title: Nocatee Parkway
